# idle_fade.scn — 活體牙: 節點 idle fade 視覺 parity (批次14 lane IF)
# 行為: 靜態節點(非 live source)60 幀無 output 更新 → bg 暗至 60%
#        live source 節點(Automation-driven)每幀 stamp → bg 維持活躍色
# TiXL: DrawNode.cs:42-50 RemapAndClamp(framesSince,0,60,1.0,0.6)
#
# 構造:
#   1. 開 compound_smoke.swproj (全靜態節點, lastUpdatePass=0)
#   2. 等 2 秒 (>60 幀 @ 60fps → 靜態節點完全 idle, bg=0.6 factor)
#   3. 截 idle_static (全靜態暗色)
#   4. Animate node:2 Radius → node:2 變 Automation-driven (live source)
#      → stampLiveLastUpdatePass 每幀更新 → idleFadeFactor 回到 1.0 (活躍亮色)
#   5. 截 after_animate → node:2 bg 比 idle_static 亮 → assert_diff 通過
#
# 鐵線驗證(值/版本鏈不變): assert_state 確認 transport state 正常
#   + 改 Radius 值截圖前後有 diff (cook 路徑沒被 idle fade 破壞)
#
# RED 證法: 移除 wait 2 (< 60 幀 → 靜態節點未 idle) + 移除 Animate 步驟
#   → idle_static 和 after_animate 顏色相同 → assert_diff FAIL
#   或: 把 assert_diff 改成 assert_same → 直接 FAIL
#
# --- 誠實弱點標注 (R-IF 附帶要求) ---
# assert_diff 比較整張 full.png (含 Inspector panel 變化):
#   假綠風險: Inspector 文字或 timeline 任何像素變化都能讓 diff 通過，
#   即使 node bg 顏色沒有正確復原。
#   → 此 scn 只能證「某個像素變了」，不能機讀確認是 node bg 亮了。
# 「Time 下游節點不假暗」的確定性驗證已由 --selftest-idlefade P5 腿蓋住
#   (computeLiveDownstreamClosure 閉包正確性 + stamp 後 Multiply.framesSince==0)。
#   scn 的角色是目視整合測試，不是下游 stamp 邏輯的唯一證明。

open app/testdata/compound_smoke.swproj

# 鐵線: transport 正常運作、值鏈沒有被 idle fade 破壞
assert_state '.transport.bpm > 0'
echo iron-line-cook-path-intact

# 等超過 60 幀讓靜態節點進入 idle 狀態
wait 2
capture full idle_static
echo idle-static-captured

# Animate node:2 (EmitterComp) 的 Radius → 變成 Automation-driven (live source)
# live source 每幀被 stampLiveLastUpdatePass 更新 → idleFadeFactor=1.0 (活躍亮色)
do click @node:2^
do rclick @param:Radius
do click @insp:Animate
echo node2-is-now-live-source

# 等幾幀讓 stamp 生效 (1 幀已夠，0.1s 安全邊際)
wait 0.5
capture full after_animate
echo after-animate-captured

# node:2 的 bg 從 idle 暗色回到活躍亮色 → 畫面必然有 diff
assert_diff idle_static
echo idle-fade-visual-verified

# 鐵線驗證: idle fade 不影響 cook 結果
# 選 node:2 → 在 Inspector 改 Radius → 截圖前後 output 視圖變化 (geometry 改了)
capture full before_param_change
do click @node:2^
do drag @param:Radius +40 +0
capture full after_param_change
assert_diff before_param_change
echo cook-path-not-broken-by-idle-fade
